Perform quantitative and qualitative data collection and analysis of program effectiveness, student learning outcomes, instructional effectiveness, as well as to support planning and decision-making;
Collaborate with faculty and staff in developing effective assessment strategies associated with student learning outcomes, creating/identifying valid and reliable assessment instruments, analyzing assessment methods and results, reporting and communicating assessment results, and preparing reports and presentations;
